article.description: Nelly Cummings had 20 points as Colgate stretched its win streak to seven games, topping Navy 70-63 on Saturday.
article.headline: Cummings scores 20 to carry Colgate over Navy 70-63
article.linkText: Cummings scores 20 to carry Colgate over Navy 70-63
article.story: ANNAPOLIS, Md. -- Nelly Cummings had 20 points as Colgate stretched its win streak to seven games, topping Navy 70-63 on Saturday. Rapolas Ivanauskas had 16 points for Colgate (13-4, 4-0 Patriot League). Jordan Burns added 13 points, six rebounds and six assists. Will Rayman had eight rebounds and three blocks for the visitors. Cam Davis had 22 points for the Midshipmen (8-7, 2-2). John Carter Jr. added 18 points. Tyler Nelson had 10 points. Colgate faces Lafayette on the road on Wednesday. Navy faces Lehigh on the road on Wednesday. --- For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP-Top25 --- This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
